  "detailed_description": "ZHUST - THE ILLUSION SOUL is third person Hack & Slash game with various combo and fast-paced attack moveset.<br><br><strong>Story</strong><br>You are \"Kan\", The Blacksmith. Who made sword for The Guardian Army. The world was peaceful. Until one day, the mysterious man appeared to Kan, He gave Kan an Illusion Material for making sword for him. But after Kan finish that swords, Chaotic story was happened.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>- Fluid combat</strong><br>Attacking, evading and casting magic. That can be done easily with no input lag.<br><br><strong>- Various combo</strong><br>Spamming attack inputs will lead to launch different combo if you already bought it.",
  "about_the_game": "ZHUST - THE ILLUSION SOUL is third person Hack & Slash game with various combo and fast-paced attack moveset.<br><br><strong>Story</strong><br>You are \"Kan\", The Blacksmith. Who made sword for The Guardian Army. The world was peaceful. Until one day, the mysterious man appeared to Kan, He gave Kan an Illusion Material for making sword for him. But after Kan finish that swords, Chaotic story was happened.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>- Fluid combat</strong><br>Attacking, evading and casting magic. That can be done easily with no input lag.<br><br><strong>- Various combo</strong><br>Spamming attack inputs will lead to launch different combo if you already bought it.",
